Blurb::
Stochastic Collocation polynomial surrogate model

Description::
Selects stochastic collocation (SC) model to use in the Bayesian
likelihood calculations. When using SC as a surrogate within the
Bayesian framework, the build points (training points) for the
stochastic collocation are constructed from a sparse grid.

